      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、お疲れ様\n一人でどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ good work.\nWhat's the matter all alone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2530.0000000000005,
          "startTime": 3.33
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.3333332999996,
          "startTime": 3.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、今度のライブ\n私の家族も観に来てくれる、って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san‚ about the upcoming live performance\nMy family will come to watch too…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.977029562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりのステージにか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the Hoshimi Festival stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7103628953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1123810529
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そう、それ\n早速、お母さんに連絡したら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… that's right.\nI immediately contacted my mom‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9457143862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "家族で観に行く、応援してる、って\nさっき……メッセ、来てた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and she said they'll come to support.\nJust got a message earlier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.045715022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7790483553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "地元のライブは久しぶりだし\n家族が来てくれるなんて……凄く、楽しみ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while since I performed locally‚ and having my family come…\nI'm really looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5758724231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1790483553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "やる気十分だな\n俺も、星見でのライブは特別に感じるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem very motivated.\nI also feel something special about performing at Hoshimi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5602276562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "星見市から始まった、サニピが\nいろんな経験を積んで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace started in Hoshimi City\nand gained various experiences…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3935609895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりという、舞台に立つ……\n凄く、エモい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now standing on the stage of the Hoshimi Festival…\nIt's really emotional…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5935609895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.460225113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの人達だけじゃなくて、地元の人達も\nいっぱい観に来てくれると思うと、嬉しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just the fans‚ but also the locals coming to watch…\nI'm happy about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.460225113,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}